         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne Botanic Garden, ¶ 20 February 1862. ¶ Esteemed Professor, ¶  ¶ I take the liberty of sending you a case of unprepared seaweeds through Dr Barlow, ¶  ship's doctor of the clipper "Donald McKa...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">62.02.20b</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Johan Areschoug</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">J. E. Areschoug brefsamling, Kungl. Vetenskapsakademien, Stockholm.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">Melbourne bot. Gart.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">/20/2/62.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Verehrter Herr Professor.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Durch Herrn Dr Barlow, Schiffsarzt des Clippers "Donald McKay" erlaube ich mir Ihnen eine Kiste unpräparirter Seetange zusenden, unter denen Sie eine reichliche Masse von Ballia Brunonis und Melobesien finden werden. Das Ganze enthält nur zartere Species, keine Fucaceen.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ich habe Dr Barlow ersucht die Kiste bei Ihrer Gesandschaft oder bei Ihrem General Consul in London abgeben zu wollen.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Mit innigster Hochachtung der Ihre</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. Mueller.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>M.D.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Herrn Prof Dr Areschoug.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne Botanic Garden,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">20 February 1862.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Esteemed Professor,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I take the liberty of sending you a case of unprepared seaweeds through Dr Barlow,<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>No biographical information found.</p>
               </note> ship's doctor of the clipper "Donald McKay"<seg style="font-style: italic; ">.</seg> You will find among them a large quantity of <name key="Ballia%20brunonis">Ballia brunonis</name> and Melobesiae. The whole contains only fine species, no <name key="Fucaceae">Fucaceae</name>.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have asked Dr Barlow to deliver the case to your Embassy or to your Consul General in London.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="de">With sincere respect your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. Mueller.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>M.D.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Professor Areschoug.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Ballia%20brunonis">Ballia brunonis</name>
            </p>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Melobesiae%20">Melobesiae </name>
            </p>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Fucaceae">Fucaceae</name>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
         </div>
